transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yeah, my name is Bill Lenson, and I've been buying the Blue Scores pills for a while, and I want to cancel the order. I've got too many pills and haven't used them.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can help you with that, sir. What is your last name and zip code?

Speaker 2: Lenson, L-E-N-S-O-N, 85298.

Speaker 1: Alrighty, so you're currently a VIP member for the Viagra AGV, sir. The moment I cancel out these orders, you won't be able to access this in the future.

Speaker 2: Are you sure you didn't want to just freeze your account out?

Speaker 1: We can always freeze it out for you, that way you can retain access to the script and not lose it.

Speaker 2: Well, what I don't want is the next order sent to me, that's all.

Speaker 1: Okay, no worries.

Speaker 2: If you want to freeze it, that's fine.

Speaker 1: I'll go ahead and freeze it out for you.

Speaker 2: Maybe I can freeze it for half a year.

Speaker 1: Call us up when you're ready to order it again, though. I'll be more than happy to help you.

Speaker 2: Alright, appreciate it. Thanks very much.

Speaker 1: Have a great day, then.

Speaker 2: Of course, bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
